ðŸ§ª Model Training Notes

The LSTM model was trained on labeled social media text dataset.

Tokenizer was fit on training text and saved using pickle.

Model saved using model.save("lstm_model.h5")

Maximum sequence length used: 100

If you want, I can generate a detailed model_training.ipynb file as well.

